title: Lydia Lunch - Honeymoon in Red
description:
<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Honeymoon_in_Red" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Honeymoon_in_Red</a> :
"Honeymoon In Red is a concept album released in 1987 as a Lydia Lunch album. Honeymoon In Red is sometimes referred to as a band or alternately as a collaboration between Lydia Lunch and The Birthday Party."

Plus Thurston Moore, J.G. Thirlwell as producer, Genevieve McGuckin...
